title: X3 Albion Prelude Update 3.0 [VIPER666]
description:
--===VIPER666===--

This will update Albion Prelude to version 3.0 (and Terran Conflict to version 3.2c)

Instructions:
1. Download & install X3.Albion.Prelude-SKIDROW (you don't need any of the updates released)
2. Extract the contents (not the folder) of this update into the game folder, overwriting existing files.
3. Enjoy your game

- if you already have X3 installed (with any SKIDROW updates), ignore step 1
- i know 3.1 is the latest update (minor fixes to the 3.0 update) but there is no release for it yet

Crack provided by DiNATyRAT

--===VIPER666===--
